**The Skybound Piglet**

In the rolling hills of Sunnydale Farm, a plump and playful pig named Percy lived life on all fours.
He loved nothing more than snuffling out juicy berries and taking leisurely strolls through the lush green fields.
While his friends would frolic in the mud, for Percy, the ultimate thrill was gazing up at the sky.
He'd watch birds soar effortlessly above, the fields, their wings beating with ease, other pigs couldn't understand.
"Why can't I do that?"
"Why can't I join them?"
Percy would ask himself, his curly tail twitching with longing.
One day, and daydreams got him into trouble.
